## 🔌 主题集成

### 注入点说明

#### head 注入点
```yaml
inject:
  head:
    # 在 </head> 标签前注入
    # 用于放置 CSS 文件
    - <link rel="stylesheet" href="/custom_components/weather/weather.css">
```

#### bottom 注入点
```yaml
inject:
  bottom:
    # 在 </body> 标签前注入
    # 用于放置 JavaScript 文件
    - <script src="/custom_components/weather/weather.js"></script>
```

### 注入顺序
```
<head>
  <!-- 主题自带 CSS -->
  <link href="/css/theme.css">

  <!-- 自定义组件 CSS（按 priority 排序）-->
  <link href="/custom_components/clock/clock.css">
  <link href="/custom_components/weather/weather.css">
</head>

<body>
  <!-- 页面内容 -->

  <!-- 自定义组件 JavaScript（按 priority 排序）-->
  <script src="/custom_components/clock/clock.js">
  <script src="/custom_components/weather/weather.js">
</body>
```

---

## ⚙️ 配置管理

### 1. 组件配置文件 (components.config.yml)

```yaml
components:
  weather:
    enable: false
    name: "Weather Component"
    description: "显示实时天气信息"
    css: "/custom_components/weather/weather.css"
    js: "/custom_components/weather/weather.js"
    priority: 1
    dependencies: []
```

### 2. 主题配置文件 (_config.butterfly.yml)

```yaml
inject:
  head:
    - <link rel="stylesheet" href="/custom_components/weather/weather.css">
  bottom:
    - <script src="/custom_components/weather/weather.js"></script>
```

### 3. 管理脚本 (manage.js)

```bash
# 启用组件
node source/custom_components/manage.js enable <component>

# 禁用组件
node source/custom_components/manage.js disable <component>

# 查看状态
node source/custom_components/manage.js status
```

